import React from 'react'
import logo from './logo.svg'
import './styles/coreStyles/App.css'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import Navbar from './components/navbar'

    <React.Fragment>
      <Navbar />
      <TitleSlider />
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default App
